data.description: LAKE CREST..One of the BEST Hoover neighborhoods! You'll love living on the quiet street of Crystal Circle. This lovely home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with a fabulous backyard space. Hardwood flooring was refinished in 2023. On the main level has tons of space: Open living area, large formal dining space, Kitchen with breakfast room, and additional room that can be an office or another living space. You will also enjoy the MAIN LEVEL GARAGE! Upstairs you'll find the Master suite with large soaking tub and walk-in shower. There is also 3 other well-appointed guest rooms with another full bathroom. Head outside to your private oasis, ready for entertaining guest! Enjoy the screened-in porch while you watch football. The home offers updates galore: Roof 2018, Exterior Paint 2021, HVAC units 2022, Water heater 2023, and newer appliances! The community has a private lake, walking trails, pool, and a PICKLEBALL COURT! WELCOME HOME!!
